<p>That should take care of the first error, so refresh. Closer - that error is gone,
but now there's an error loading the <code>wdt.xml</code> routing file. Again, this makes sense:
we're still loading some routes from <code>@WebProfilerBundle</code>, which simply doesn't exist
in the <code>prod</code> environment:</p>
